3. From the context menu, click on the "B" button. This button is located at the top of the screen and is used to underline the selected text.
4. Alternatively, you can also highlight the text by clicking and dragging your mouse over it. Once the text is highlighted, click on the "U" button at the top of the screen to underline it.

